Pwrake demo : Montage Workflow Moniter

  Montage website : http://montage.ipac.caltech.edu/

1. Download Montage source

 * visit http://montage.ipac.caltech.edu/docs/download.html
 * download Montage_v3.3.tar.gz

2. Compile Montage

  $ tar xvzf Montage_v3.3.tar.gz
  $ cd Montage_v3.3
  $ make
  $ cd ..

3. Set command search PATH

 * bash
  $ export PATH=`pwd`/Montage_v3.3/bin:$PATH

 * csh
  % setenv PATH `pwd`/Montage_v3.3/bin:$PATH

4. Compile & Install Ruby/METIS

 * see http://github.com/masa16/ruby-metis

5. Edit nodefiles

  $ cd nodes
  $ vi ...

6. Run servelet

  $ ruby servlet.rb
